 <i>made a miracle reality.</i>

00:07:39.894 --> 00:07:41.796 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-You're awesome Tsubasa!!

00:07:41.829 --> 00:07:43.397 position:30% line:83% align:start
That's my son!
Excellent job!

00:07:43.431 --> 00:07:44.632 position:24% line:89% align:start
Great job, my love.

00:07:44.665 --> 00:07:46.100 position:13% line:83% align:start
Finally, we really did it,
Coach!

00:07:46.133 --> 00:07:47.101 position:38% line:89% align:start
You did.

00:07:47.134 --> 00:07:48.269 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-You were amazing!

00:07:48.302 --> 00:07:49.804 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Incredible!
-Beautiful goal!

00:07:49.837 --> 00:07:51.973 position:27% line:83% align:start
Great job, team!
Very well done!

00:07:53.207 --> 00:07:54.208 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Well done, son.</i>

00:07:58.112 --> 00:07:59.880 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sobs]

00:07:59.914 --> 00:08:01.282 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Mr. Mikami]
 <i>You did well, kid.</i>

00:08:01.315 --> 00:08:03.483 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Defending that goal</i>
 <i>was impossible.</i>

00:08:06.287 --> 00:08:08.022 position:27% line:89% align:start
Captain... Uh...

00:08:08.055 --> 00:08:09.824 position:21% line:89% align:start
We're sorry, Captain.

00:08:09.857 --> 00:08:13.361 position:19% line:83% align:start
We're so sorry for not
covering them well, Captain.

00:08:13.394 --> 00:08:14.862 position:13% line:89% align:start
What are you talking about?

00:08:14.895 --> 00:08:15.830 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:08:15.863 --> 00:08:18.366 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's not like this game
is over yet, guys.

00:08:18.399 --> 00:08:19.900 position:19% line:89% align:start
We can still win this.

00:08:19.934 --> 00:08:20.868 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-Yeah!

00:08:20.901 --> 00:08:23.070 position:24% line:83% align:start
We still have time
to score on them.

00:08:23.104 --> 00:08:24.472 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's go for a goal.

00:08:24.505 --> 00:08:25.539 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:08:26.841 --> 00:08:29.777 position:13% line:83% align:start
[commentator] <i>This match is</i>
 <i>not for the faint of heart.</i>

00:08:29.810 --> 00:08:32.246 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>No one knows</i>
 <i>what'll happen now.</i>

00:08:32.279 --> 00:08:34.248 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>There's two minutes left.</i>

00:08:34.281 --> 00:08:36.250 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mamoru]
 <i>We'll score this time...</i>

00:08:36.283 --> 00:08:37.385 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>for the Captain.</i>

