[whistle]

00:08:38.352 --> 00:08:39.553 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:08:40.121 --> 00:08:40.588 position:30% line:89% align:start
Let's go, team!

00:08:40.621 --> 00:08:42.056 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:08:42.089 --> 00:08:45.292 position:10% line:83% align:start
[commentator] <i>You won't want</i>
 <i>to miss this match's ending.</i>

00:08:45.326 --> 00:08:47.728 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Shutetsu initiates</i>
 <i>their attack.</i>

00:08:47.762 --> 00:08:49.330 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>But they lose the ball.</i>

00:08:49.363 --> 00:08:50.998 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>And now Teppei gets it back!</i>

00:08:52.366 --> 00:08:53.667 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>These last few minutes</i>
 <i>have been</i>

00:08:53.701 --> 00:08:56.404 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>a constant back and forth</i>
 <i>between the two teams.</i>

00:08:56.437 --> 00:08:57.571 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>The players are exhausted,</i>

00:08:57.605 --> 00:09:00.474 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>but they keep giving it</i>
 <i>their 100%.</i>

00:09:00.509 --> 00:09:02.443 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>There is less than</i>
 <i>a minute on the clock.</i>

00:09:02.476 --> 00:09:03.677 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>And due to regulations,</i>

00:09:03.711 --> 00:09:06.180 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>there will be</i>
 <i>no more overtime.</i>

00:09:06.213 --> 00:09:08.149 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cheers]

00:09:08.182 --> 00:09:10.217 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's win, Shutetsu!

00:09:10.251 --> 00:09:12.720 position:19% line:83% align:start
[commentator] <i>And now,</i>
 <i>Teppei receives the ball.</i>

00:09:12.753 --> 00:09:15.189 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>But two defenders</i>
 <i>are blocking him</i>

00:09:15.222 --> 00:09:16.857 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>from getting to the goal.</i>

00:09:16.891 --> 00:09:17.958 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:09:17.992 --> 00:09:19.528 position:33% line:83% align:start
[commentator]
 <i>He gets a chance to kick,</i>

00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:21.896 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>but it lands in</i>
 <i>the goalkeeper's knuckles.</i>

00:09:21.929 --> 00:09:23.664 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[commentator] <i>Tsubasa kicks</i>

00:09:23.697 --> 00:09:25.066 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>the ball off</i>
 <i>the penalty area.</i>

00:09:25.099 --> 00:09:27.301 position:30% line:83% align:start
Attack, Shingo.
Go get the ball from him.

00:09:27.334 --> 00:09:28.569 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:09:28.602 --> 00:09:30.337 position:19% line:83% align:start
[commentator] <i>A sliding</i>
 <i>tackle from Shingo!</i>

00:09:30.371 --> 00:09:31.806 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Akiyoshi]
Great, now's our chance.

00:09:31.839 --> 00:09:32.740 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:32.773 --> 00:09:33.707 position:33% line:83% align:start
[commentator]
 <i>Taro quickly recovers</i>

00:09:33.741 --> 00:09:35.009 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>the ball for his team.</i>

00:09:35.042 --> 00:09:37.311 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>However, there isn't</i>
 <i>enough time on the clock.</i>

00:09:37.344 --> 00:09:39.046 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's yours, Tsubasa!

00:09:40.181 --> 00:09:41.182 position:21% line:89% align:start
I won't let you down!

00:09:41.215 --> 00:09:42.583 position:16% line:83% align:start
[commentator] <i>The ref is</i>
 <i>checking his watch.</i>

00:09:42.616 --> 00:09:43.818 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll take care
of him myself.

00:09:43.851 --> 00:09:45.119 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Step aside!
-Huh?

00:09:46.687 --> 00:09:47.788 position:33% line:83% align:start
[commentator]
 <i>Tsubasa and Genzo</i>

00:09:47.822 --> 00:09:49.924 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>both go directly</i>
 <i>towards the ball.</i>

00:09:49.957 --> 00:09:51.926 position:30% line:89% align:start
You can do it!

00:09:51.959 --> 00:09:54.128 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:09:54.161 --> 00:09:55.396 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:09:55.429 --> 00:09:56.630 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:09:56.664 --> 00:09:57.932 position:33% line:83% align:start
[commentator]
 <i>Tsubasa and Genzo</i>

00:09:57.965 --> 00:09:59.967 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>jump at the exact same time.</i>

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:03.003 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is the last play</i>
 <i>of the game!</i>

00:10:08.142 --> 00:10:10.111 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:10:11.312 --> 00:10:15.182 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:10:16.417 --> 00:10:18.018 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-Ah!

00:10:18.052 --> 00:10:19.053 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:10:21.122 --> 00:10:22.189 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:10:24.024 --> 00:10:25.226 position:33% line:83% align:start
[commentator]
 <i>Goal post.</i>

00:10:25.259 --> 00:10:27.194 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>It hit the goal post</i>
 <i>and went out of bounds.</i>

00:10:27.228 --> 00:10:28.696 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:10:28.729 --> 00:10:29.830 position:33% line:83% align:start
[commentator]
 <i>It's all over.</i>

00:10:29.864 --> 00:10:31.065 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>The ref blows the whistle</i>

00:10:31.098 --> 00:10:32.700 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>signaling the end</i>
 <i>of the match.</i>

00:10:32.733 --> 00:10:34.335 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>The final score is 2 to 2.</i>
-[panting]

00:10:34.368 --> 00:10:36.837 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even with the overwhelming</i>
 <i>action in overtime,</i>

00:10:36.871 --> 00:10:39.073 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>no team was able to</i>
 <i>close out the match.</i>

00:10:39.106 --> 00:10:41.675 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Both teams have two goals</i>
 <i>in their favor.</i>

00:10:41.709 --> 00:10:44.111 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is the second time</i>
 <i>in 26 tournaments</i>

00:10:44.145 --> 00:10:46.447 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>between schools</i>
 <i>that a match ends</i>

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:48.249 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>with an incredible tie.</i>

00:10:53.053 --> 00:10:54.054 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:54.589 --> 00:10:56.023 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:10:56.824 --> 00:10:58.893 position:19% line:83% align:start
You played really well,
Tsubasa.

00:10:58.926 --> 00:11:00.227 position:35% line:83% align:start
Thank you.
So did you.

00:11:01.962 --> 00:11:02.863 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:11:03.330 --> 00:11:04.665 position:27% line:89% align:start
Good job, Genzo.

00:11:09.470 --> 00:11:11.172 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, it's finally over.

00:11:12.072 --> 00:11:13.508 position:33% line:89% align:start
Ouch my back.

00:11:13.542 --> 00:11:15.409 position:27% line:83% align:start
I've never played
such an intense game

00:11:15.442 --> 00:11:16.477 position:33% line:83% align:start
like this one
my whole life.

00:11:16.511 --> 00:11:17.845 position:30% line:83% align:start
Neither have I.
It all hurts.

00:11:17.878 --> 00:11:21.148 position:13% line:83% align:start
It feels like my lungs are
ripping out of my chest.

00:11:21.182 --> 00:11:23.150 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey, great game.

00:11:23.184 --> 00:11:23.851 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:11:23.884 --> 00:11:24.818 position:16% line:89% align:start
I never thought you guys

00:11:24.852 --> 00:11:26.621 position:30% line:83% align:start
could actually
play like that.

00:11:26.655 --> 00:11:29.123 position:30% line:83% align:start
I gotta admit,
you improved a lot.

00:11:29.156 --> 00:11:30.024 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[cheers]

00:11:30.057 --> 00:11:31.759 position:30% line:83% align:start
You all played
incredibly well!

00:11:31.792 --> 00:11:32.860 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:11:32.893 --> 00:11:34.962 position:21% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu and Shutetsu
are the best!

00:11:34.995 --> 00:11:37.231 position:35% line:83% align:start
You gave us
an amazing match.

00:11:37.264 --> 00:11:38.732 position:16% line:89% align:start
You guys aren't mediocre.

00:11:38.766 --> 00:11:41.603 position:21% line:83% align:start
Everyone in the city
is proud of you!

00:11:41.636 --> 00:11:43.470 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:11:43.505 --> 00:11:45.339 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:11:45.372 --> 00:11:47.007 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey, Tsubasa...

00:11:47.041 --> 00:11:47.741 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:48.610 --> 00:11:50.711 position:27% line:83% align:start
You guys gave us
an incredible game.

00:11:50.744 --> 00:11:52.012 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:11:52.046 --> 00:11:56.050 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:11:56.083 --> 00:11:57.151 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:11:57.184 --> 00:11:59.453 position:27% line:83% align:start
Thank you so much
for cheering us on!

00:11:59.486 --> 00:12:00.555 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:12:00.589 --> 00:12:02.189 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:12:02.223 --> 00:12:03.692 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, Tsubasa.

00:12:03.724 --> 00:12:05.726 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

00:12:05.759 --> 00:12:08.395 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Hey, don't cry.
-[chuckles]

00:12:08.429 --> 00:12:09.730 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa.
-Huh?

00:12:09.763 --> 00:12:11.765 position:10% line:89% align:start
That was an excellent match.

00:12:11.799 --> 00:12:13.000 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you!

00:12:14.235 --> 00:12:16.837 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Roberto] <i>Although it's just</i>
 <i>the beginning.</i>

00:12:16.870 --> 00:12:18.939 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>Your career</i>
 <i>as a soccer player...</i>

00:12:18.973 --> 00:12:20.941 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>has just begun its journey.</i>

00:12:32.987 --> 00:12:34.021 position:35% line:83% align:start
[narrator]
 <i>We'll be right back</i>

00:12:34.054 --> 00:12:35.990 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>with Captain Tsubasa.</i>

00:12:40.027 --> 00:12:41.462 position:35% line:83% align:start
[narrator]
 <i>And we're back!</i>

00:12:46.300 --> 00:12:47.768 position:41% line:89% align:start
[hums]

00:12:48.570 --> 00:12:50.771 position:44% line:83% align:start
Huh?
Hi, good morning, Roberto.

00:12:50.804 --> 00:12:52.006 position:21% line:89% align:start
Good morning, Ma'am.

00:12:53.474 --> 00:12:55.677 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey, um, where is Tsubasa?

00:12:55.710 --> 00:12:57.011 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, take a wild guess.

00:12:57.044 --> 00:12:58.879 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's outside playing
in the court.

00:12:58.912 --> 00:13:00.080 position:27% line:83% align:start
He just finished
a match

00:13:00.114 --> 00:13:01.683 position:30% line:83% align:start
yet he's still
playing soccer.

00:13:01.716 --> 00:13:03.618 position:10% line:89% align:start
That kid does not get tired.

00:13:03.652 --> 00:13:04.918 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:13:07.656 --> 00:13:08.623 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:13:08.657 --> 00:13:09.790 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Take it away from me.
-Oh yeah?

00:13:09.823 --> 00:13:10.824 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll show you.
[laugh]

00:13:10.858 --> 00:13:13.427 position:13% line:83% align:start
The two of them never stop,
do they?

00:13:13.460 --> 00:13:14.828 position:19% line:89% align:start
And here I am exhausted

00:13:14.862 --> 00:13:16.297 position:30% line:83% align:start
from the match
we recently played.

00:13:16.330 --> 00:13:18.866 position:13% line:83% align:start
I feel like we just played
this morning.

00:13:18.899 --> 00:13:21.736 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wonder who's better
between them.

00:13:21.770 --> 00:13:22.836 position:33% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

00:13:22.870 --> 00:13:24.405 position:33% line:83% align:start
They're both
good at dribbling...

00:13:24.438 --> 00:13:27.074 position:24% line:83% align:start
but I think Tsubasa
is better at shooting.

00:13:27.107 --> 00:13:28.909 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I think you're right.

00:13:28.942 --> 00:13:31.378 position:21% line:83% align:start
And...now for Taro's
surprise kick.

00:13:31.412 --> 00:13:32.379 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:13:33.480 --> 00:13:34.616 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Whoa!
-Whoa!

00:13:34.649 --> 00:13:36.183 position:21% line:83% align:start
What were you saying,
Kenichi?

00:13:36.216 --> 00:13:37.451 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:13:37.484 --> 00:13:38.620 position:13% line:89% align:start
That doesn't really matter.

00:13:38.653 --> 00:13:39.920 position:13% line:89% align:start
If we have the two of them,

00:13:39.953 --> 00:13:42.489 position:21% line:83% align:start
we'll be able to play
in the national tournament.

00:13:42.524 --> 00:13:44.158 position:16% line:89% align:start
Yeah, if we beat Shutetsu

00:13:44.191 --> 00:13:45.694 position:33% line:83% align:start
in the single
elimination phase,

00:13:45.727 --> 00:13:47.328 position:35% line:83% align:start
we'll go to
the national tournament.

00:13:47.361 --> 00:13:48.763 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Ryo] I don't think
you'll be able to.

00:13:48.797 --> 00:13:49.997 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:13:50.632 --> 00:13:51.832 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tsuyoshi]
Hi, Ryo!

00:13:52.366 --> 00:13:52.966 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey there.

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:53.768 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why did you say that, Ryo?

00:13:53.802 --> 00:13:54.902 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Hey, looks like
-Yeah,

00:13:54.935 --> 00:13:55.869 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Ryo came back.
-what's wrong with you?

00:13:55.903 --> 00:13:57.137 position:35% line:83% align:start
Why're you
underestimating us?

00:13:57.171 --> 00:13:58.038 position:35% line:89% align:start
Calm down.

00:13:58.072 --> 00:13:59.473 position:24% line:83% align:start
I meant to say that
we won't all go to

00:13:59.507 --> 00:14:00.941 position:16% line:89% align:start
the national tournament.

00:14:00.974 --> 00:14:03.310 position:21% line:83% align:start
The city of Nankatsu
will make a new soccer team.

00:14:03.344 --> 00:14:06.080 position:13% line:83% align:start
The best local players will
be chosen to play together.

00:14:06.113 --> 00:14:07.481 position:16% line:89% align:start
The best players you say?

00:14:07.515 --> 00:14:08.616 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's all this?

00:14:08.650 --> 00:14:10.250 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey there, Tsubasa.

00:14:10.284 --> 00:14:12.353 position:41% line:83% align:start
Before,
in the elimination phase,

00:14:12.386 --> 00:14:13.120 position:16% line:89% align:start
the matches were between

00:14:13.153 --> 00:14:14.988 position:24% line:83% align:start
all of the schools
of the city.

00:14:15.022 --> 00:14:17.891 position:19% line:83% align:start
But this year, they've
set up a different system.

00:14:17.925 --> 00:14:19.860 position:19% line:83% align:start
All of the best players
from all the schools

00:14:19.893 --> 00:14:22.162 position:24% line:83% align:start
will be in a single
Nankatsu team.

00:14:23.297 --> 00:14:25.265 position:21% line:83% align:start
It was made this way
so we can be up to par

00:14:25.299 --> 00:14:26.634 position:30% line:83% align:start
with the other
districts' teams,

00:14:26.668 --> 00:14:27.935 position:38% line:83% align:start
you know,
the ones taking part

00:14:27.968 --> 00:14:29.537 position:13% line:89% align:start
in the national tournament.

00:14:29.571 --> 00:14:31.205 position:38% line:83% align:start
So then,
there'll be a new team

00:14:31.238 --> 00:14:33.508 position:21% line:83% align:start
that combines all of
Nankatsu's schools?

00:14:33.541 --> 00:14:34.475 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:14:34.509 --> 00:14:36.343 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you want to go to
the national tournament,

00:14:36.377 --> 00:14:39.313 position:13% line:83% align:start
you'll have to be chosen to
play for the new city team.

00:14:39.346 --> 00:14:41.649 position:13% line:83% align:start
The tryouts are very soon,
so be ready.

00:14:41.683 --> 00:14:42.416 position:27% line:89% align:start
How soon is that?

00:14:42.449 --> 00:14:43.551 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's great.

00:14:43.585 --> 00:14:46.086 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll try my hardest to go
to the national tournament.

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.321 position:21% line:89% align:start
Be realistic, Manabu.

00:14:47.354 --> 00:14:49.423 position:16% line:83% align:start
You couldn't even make it
to the bench of the team.

00:14:49.456 --> 00:14:52.493 position:13% line:83% align:start
Of course I can, you dummy.
We tied with Shutetsu.

00:14:52.527 --> 00:14:54.027 position:19% line:89% align:start
Nothing is impossible.

00:14:54.061 --> 00:14:56.463 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yeah, all we need to do
is practice some more.

00:14:56.497 --> 00:14:58.767 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's exactly it.
If we work our hardest,

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:00.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
we'll be sure to make
the tryouts.

00:15:00.502 --> 00:15:02.369 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:15:02.403 --> 00:15:03.805 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:15:03.838 --> 00:15:05.205 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Who would've guessed it?</i>

00:15:05.239 --> 00:15:08.342 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Their last match gave them</i>
 <i>confidence in themselves.</i>

00:15:08.375 --> 00:15:09.276 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>And me too.</i>

00:15:10.310 --> 00:15:13.380 position:27% line:83% align:start
Roberto, tell me.
What do you plan to do now?

00:15:13.414 --> 00:15:14.348 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well, to be honest,

00:15:14.381 --> 00:15:16.518 position:13% line:83% align:start
I thought about going back
to Brazil.

00:15:16.551 --> 00:15:17.217 position:33% line:89% align:start
I understand.

00:15:17.985 --> 00:15:19.319 position:30% line:83% align:start
Although I was
hoping that...

00:15:19.353 --> 00:15:20.254 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh no, Captain,

00:15:20.287 --> 00:15:21.756 position:27% line:83% align:start
you don't have to
worry about it.

00:15:21.790 --> 00:15:24.091 position:33% line:83% align:start
I assure you,
it won't happen again.

00:15:24.124 --> 00:15:25.259 position:13% line:89% align:start
What are you talking about?

00:15:25.292 --> 00:15:27.928 position:41% line:83% align:start
Well...
you'll see, Mrs. Ozora.

00:15:27.961 --> 00:15:31.098 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm talking about how
the Captain and I first met.

00:15:33.835 --> 00:15:35.102 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Roberto]
That day, I was...

00:15:35.135 --> 00:15:36.236 position:24% line:89% align:start
severely depressed.

00:15:37.104 --> 00:15:38.673 position:24% line:83% align:start
I couldn't swallow
the horrible news

00:15:38.706 --> 00:15:40.775 position:13% line:89% align:start
about my eyesight problem.

00:15:40.809 --> 00:15:43.444 position:21% line:83% align:start
So I decided to drown
my sorrows away.

00:15:46.947 --> 00:15:50.685 position:16% line:83% align:start
I went as far as to think
my life had no meaning.

00:15:50.718 --> 00:15:52.019 position:21% line:89% align:start
But at that moment...

00:15:53.521 --> 00:15:54.589 position:44% line:89% align:start
Aagh!

00:15:54.622 --> 00:15:57.024 position:19% line:83% align:start
Captain, look, I think
someone jumped in the water.

00:15:57.057 --> 00:15:58.058 position:30% line:89% align:start
What'd you say?

00:15:58.091 --> 00:16:00.093 position:30% line:83% align:start
That can't be.
We have to save him!

00:16:01.228 --> 00:16:03.598 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Roberto]
Captain Ozora saved my life.

00:16:03.631 --> 00:16:06.200 position:24% line:83% align:start
Shortly afterwards,
he recommended I come here

00:16:06.233 --> 00:16:08.670 position:30% line:83% align:start
to see the best
ophthalmologist and well...

00:16:08.703 --> 00:16:11.539 position:10% line:83% align:start
in the end, it didn't really
help my situation.

00:16:11.573 --> 00:16:13.908 position:21% line:83% align:start
I could never imagine
that not being able to play

00:16:13.942 --> 00:16:15.877 position:24% line:83% align:start
could drive someone
to that extreme.

00:16:15.910 --> 00:16:18.880 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa lives for soccer
just like I do.

00:16:18.913 --> 00:16:20.314 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hmm...
-Hmm...

00:16:20.347 --> 00:16:22.784 position:21% line:83% align:start
Your family has been
so good to me, Captain,

00:16:22.817 --> 00:16:25.219 position:30% line:83% align:start
that I feel bad
saying this, but...

00:16:25.252 --> 00:16:28.489 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'd like to ask for
a special favor.

00:16:28.523 --> 00:16:29.524 position:27% line:89% align:start
A special favor?

00:16:31.391 --> 00:16:32.560 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:16:32.594 --> 00:16:33.494 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:16:34.094 --> 00:16:35.630 position:19% line:89% align:start
Excellent work, Genzo.

00:16:35.663 --> 00:16:36.898 position:21% line:89% align:start
We're done for today.

00:16:36.931 --> 00:16:38.398 position:33% line:89% align:start
Mr. Mikami...

00:16:38.432 --> 00:16:39.299 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm not tired yet.

00:16:39.333 --> 00:16:40.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm sure that Tsubasa
and the rest

00:16:40.502 --> 00:16:42.670 position:19% line:83% align:start
are training right now
at this moment.

00:16:42.704 --> 00:16:44.204 position:24% line:83% align:start
Your body is still
recovering

00:16:44.238 --> 00:16:46.073 position:30% line:83% align:start
from the match
against Nankatsu.

00:16:46.106 --> 00:16:47.675 position:27% line:83% align:start
I don't want you
getting hurt.

00:16:47.709 --> 00:16:48.710 position:33% line:89% align:start
I understand.

00:16:49.443 --> 00:16:50.778 position:33% line:89% align:start
Master Genzo.

00:16:51.445 --> 00:16:52.647 position:33% line:89% align:start
Master Genzo.

00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:53.882 position:33% line:83% align:start
There's mail
waiting for you.

00:16:53.915 --> 00:16:55.449 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's your magazine.

00:17:00.387 --> 00:17:01.623 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:17:01.656 --> 00:17:02.690 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's wrong, my child?

00:17:02.724 --> 00:17:05.058 position:13% line:83% align:start
Find an interesting article
on the front page?

00:17:05.092 --> 00:17:06.126 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm very sorry.

00:17:06.159 --> 00:17:08.495 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'll be back.
I have to go.

00:17:08.530 --> 00:17:12.199 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chatter]

00:17:12.232 --> 00:17:13.300 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
Aw, damn it!

00:17:14.234 --> 00:17:17.070 position:21% line:83% align:start
[growl] I want to be
out there playing.

00:17:17.104 --> 00:17:18.706 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why don't you heal already?

00:17:19.707 --> 00:17:21.408 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:17:21.441 --> 00:17:22.476 position:33% line:89% align:start
My poor foot.

00:17:22.510 --> 00:17:23.477 position:38% line:83% align:start
[wincing]
Oh!

00:17:23.511 --> 00:17:25.078 position:41% line:89% align:start
[pants]

00:17:25.112 --> 00:17:26.714 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
Oh, hi there, Genzo.

00:17:26.748 --> 00:17:28.650 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm guessing you already
know about the new team

00:17:28.683 --> 00:17:29.617 position:19% line:89% align:start
for the national team.

00:17:29.651 --> 00:17:32.219 position:19% line:83% align:start
Maybe we'll be playing
together, you and I.

00:17:32.252 --> 00:17:33.320 position:30% line:83% align:start
The tie breaker
will have to wait.

00:17:33.353 --> 00:17:34.756 position:24% line:83% align:start
That doesn't matter
right now!

00:17:34.789 --> 00:17:36.189 position:13% line:89% align:start
Roberto Hongo, where is he?

00:17:36.223 --> 00:17:38.392 position:30% line:83% align:start
What's got you
so jumpy, huh?

00:17:38.425 --> 00:17:40.360 position:13% line:83% align:start
Roberto didn't come today.
Is something wrong?

00:17:40.394 --> 00:17:43.063 position:16% line:83% align:start
Then that means, you guys
haven't found out, have you?

00:17:43.096 --> 00:17:44.164 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:17:44.933 --> 00:17:46.534 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Found out about what?
-[growl]

00:17:46.568 --> 00:17:49.202 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you mean?
You have to know.

00:17:49.236 --> 00:17:51.171 position:41% line:83% align:start
[growl]
Roberto Hongo...

00:17:51.204 --> 00:17:53.541 position:21% line:83% align:start
won't play soccer for
the rest of his life.

00:17:53.575 --> 00:17:55.743 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Huh? Roberto?</i>

00:17:55.777 --> 00:17:57.477 position:19% line:89% align:start
Right there, read that.

00:17:57.512 --> 00:17:58.846 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:17:59.581 --> 00:18:00.080 position:30% line:89% align:start
What'd you say?

00:18:01.248 --> 00:18:02.382 position:13% line:83% align:start
-But why would he do that?
-But why would he do that?

00:18:02.416 --> 00:18:04.351 position:13% line:89% align:start
Retinal detachment is why.

00:18:04.384 --> 00:18:05.452 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-That doesn't make sense.

00:18:05.485 --> 00:18:07.055 position:27% line:83% align:start
He plays with us
all the time.

00:18:07.087 --> 00:18:08.388 position:33% line:83% align:start
Don't compare
a professional match

00:18:08.422 --> 00:18:10.324 position:21% line:83% align:start
with elementary kids
playing soccer.

00:18:10.357 --> 00:18:12.092 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Genzo] A professional
player can't play

00:18:12.125 --> 00:18:13.728 position:27% line:83% align:start
if they're not in
optimal conditions

00:18:13.761 --> 00:18:15.663 position:33% line:83% align:start
much less be
the team captain.

00:18:15.697 --> 00:18:16.731 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>This can't be.</i>

00:18:17.497 --> 00:18:19.132 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uh...
-Where are you going?

00:18:19.166 --> 00:18:22.169 position:16% line:83% align:start
[pants] I have to go talk
to Roberto.

00:18:22.202 --> 00:18:23.370 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Ah...
-Ah...

00:18:23.403 --> 00:18:24.204 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:18:24.237 --> 00:18:26.440 position:35% line:83% align:start
All right,
we'll go see him too.

00:18:29.844 --> 00:18:30.812 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why is he retiring?</i>

00:18:32.179 --> 00:18:34.849 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Roberto] <i>Remember this,</i>
 <i>you should all be friends.</i>

00:18:36.249 --> 00:18:38.753 position:16% line:89% align:start
He won't ever play again.

00:18:38.786 --> 00:18:39.787 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-What?!

00:18:39.821 --> 00:18:40.922 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're joking right?

00:18:40.955 --> 00:18:42.389 position:27% line:83% align:start
Please, Captain.
And ma'am...

00:18:42.422 --> 00:18:45.359 position:27% line:83% align:start
I promise you...
that I'll make your son...

00:18:45.392 --> 00:18:47.294 position:38% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa,
into the best soccer player

00:18:47.327 --> 00:18:49.229 position:16% line:89% align:start
the world has ever seen.

00:18:49.262 --> 00:18:50.330 position:30% line:89% align:start
Please let me.

00:18:50.364 --> 00:18:52.299 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Roberto!
-I'm begging you.

00:18:52.332 --> 00:18:54.434 position:16% line:83% align:start
Allow me to take your son
to Brazil.

00:18:54.468 --> 00:18:55.503 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Huh?!</i>

00:18:55.536 --> 00:18:56.504 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:18:56.838 --> 00:18:57.805 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa.

00:18:59.574 --> 00:19:00.608 position:35% line:89% align:start
Roberto...

00:19:00.642 --> 00:19:01.576 position:24% line:89% align:start
Tell me one thing.

00:19:01.609 --> 00:19:04.679 position:16% line:83% align:start
Is it true you won't ever
play soccer again?

00:19:04.712 --> 00:19:05.613 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's right, kid.

00:19:05.647 --> 00:19:08.650 position:33% line:83% align:start
So that means
your eye problem is real?

00:19:08.683 --> 00:19:09.817 position:41% line:89% align:start
It is.

00:19:09.851 --> 00:19:11.218 position:21% line:89% align:start
And unfortunately...

00:19:11.251 --> 00:19:13.855 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll never be able to
play soccer again.

00:19:13.888 --> 00:19:14.889 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:19:18.158 --> 00:19:18.458 position:35% line:89% align:start
Roberto...

00:19:19.493 --> 00:19:21.896 position:24% line:83% align:start
Brazil is a country
full of soccer, isn't it?

00:19:21.929 --> 00:19:22.664 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:19:22.697 --> 00:19:23.698 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:19:23.731 --> 00:19:26.500 position:24% line:83% align:start
Everybody in Brazil
lives and breathes soccer.

00:19:26.534 --> 00:19:29.704 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's a big part of
our everyday lives.

00:19:29.737 --> 00:19:30.470 position:35% line:89% align:start
So then...

00:19:31.271 --> 00:19:33.541 position:19% line:83% align:start
I want to go to Brazil
with you!

00:19:33.574 --> 00:19:34.542 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:19:34.575 --> 00:19:35.576 position:30% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, but...

00:19:37.111 --> 00:19:38.946 position:33% line:83% align:start
In that case,
we should take advantage

00:19:38.980 --> 00:19:41.248 position:19% line:83% align:start
of the time you're here
with us.

00:19:41.281 --> 00:19:42.550 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-Ah!

00:19:43.250 --> 00:19:44.652 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yes, that's true.

00:19:45.252 --> 00:19:46.253 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, we'll just have to

00:19:46.286 --> 00:19:48.188 position:33% line:83% align:start
train harder
than ever before.

00:19:48.221 --> 00:19:49.924 position:24% line:83% align:start
We'll train so that
we can be with you

00:19:49.957 --> 00:19:51.491 position:13% line:89% align:start
in the national tournament.

00:19:51.526 --> 00:19:52.927 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Of course we will!
-Of course we will!

00:19:52.960 --> 00:19:53.928 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm...

00:19:59.767 --> 00:20:02.170 position:13% line:83% align:start
[narrator] <i>And so, the day</i>
 <i>to tryout for the team</i>

00:20:02.202 --> 00:20:03.638 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>that will represent</i>
 <i>Nankatsu city</i>

00:20:03.671 --> 00:20:06.306 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>in the national</i>
 <i>tournament finally arrived.</i>

00:20:06.339 --> 00:20:08.241 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>All of the schools'</i>
 <i>teams in the city</i>

00:20:08.275 --> 00:20:10.210 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>are here to demonstrate</i>
 <i>their worth.</i>

00:20:10.243 --> 00:20:12.180 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>The trainer Shiroyama</i>
 <i>and the judges</i>

00:20:12.212 --> 00:20:13.246 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>will take five minutes</i>

00:20:13.280 --> 00:20:15.449 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>to evaluate each</i>
 <i>individual player.</i>

00:20:15.482 --> 00:20:16.283 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:17.151 --> 00:20:18.251 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[narrator] <i>Genzo, and each</i>
-Taki!

00:20:18.285 --> 00:20:19.654 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>and every player in town...</i>
-Not yet!

00:20:19.687 --> 00:20:22.123 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>want to show off their</i>
 <i>abilities in the field</i>

00:20:22.156 --> 00:20:24.525 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>to be a part of</i>
 <i>the newly founded team.</i>

00:20:24.559 --> 00:20:25.893 position:24% line:83% align:start
The way the tryouts
are going,

00:20:25.927 --> 00:20:26.794 position:16% line:89% align:start
I have a feeling the team

00:20:26.828 --> 00:20:28.763 position:19% line:83% align:start
will have a lot of kids
from Shutetsu.

00:20:28.796 --> 00:20:30.363 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Shiroyama] It's still
too early to tell.

00:20:30.397 --> 00:20:31.966 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-There's many more players

00:20:31.999 --> 00:20:33.067 position:33% line:89% align:start
to evaluate.

00:20:33.101 --> 00:20:34.135 position:16% line:89% align:start
I know we'll find talent

00:20:34.168 --> 00:20:36.637 position:27% line:83% align:start
that's up to par
to Shutetsu.

00:20:36.671 --> 00:20:39.140 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:20:39.173 --> 00:20:40.174 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:20:40.208 --> 00:20:41.374 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:20:44.545 --> 00:20:45.713 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:45.747 --> 00:20:46.748 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:48.149 --> 00:20:49.550 position:27% line:83% align:start
He made that shot
in mid-air!

00:20:49.584 --> 00:20:51.853 position:33% line:83% align:start
That kid has
an incredible shot.

00:20:51.886 --> 00:20:53.755 position:13% line:89% align:start
Ugh! It had to be Tsubasa.

00:20:53.788 --> 00:20:54.655 position:24% line:89% align:start
That was excellent.

00:20:54.689 --> 00:20:56.256 position:21% line:83% align:start
I think I just found
our main striker

00:20:56.289 --> 00:20:58.092 position:33% line:83% align:start
for the team.
It's him!

00:20:58.126 --> 00:20:59.259 position:38% line:89% align:start
Roberto!

00:20:59.292 --> 00:21:00.661 position:38% line:83% align:start
We'll win
the national tournament,

00:21:00.695 --> 00:21:03.531 position:19% line:83% align:start
and then we're going to
go to Brazil.

00:21:03.564 --> 00:21:04.565 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:21:05.666 --> 00:21:07.034 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hello, everyone.

00:21:07.068 --> 00:21:08.136 position:24% line:89% align:start
I want to thank you

00:21:08.169 --> 00:21:10.238 position:27% line:83% align:start
for participating
in the tryouts.

00:21:10.270 --> 00:21:12.140 position:30% line:83% align:start
Our judges were
very impressed

00:21:12.173 --> 00:21:12.940 position:24% line:83% align:start
by your outstanding
performance.

00:21:12.974 --> 00:21:14.041 position:27% line:89% align:start
Shut up already.

